profile:
MY CITY MOVERS LTD  is one of the fastest growing  companies in British Columbia, all due to the exceptional service at a very affordable price.  As Movers in Vancouver we provide packing services, local and long distance moving, delivery services within the Lower Mainland, storage, overnight storage and more..Our moving team is dedicated to working with you personally form the early stages of your move to move in day, we ensure a smooth and stress free relocation.
Please call us anytime!

***

Toll free: 1833-MCM-MOVE/1-833-626-6683

Cell: 778-886-7271
